\c 83
\s Munyengetero kuti Mwari arwire vanhu vake
\s Rwiyo, Pisarema raAsafi.
\p
\v 83
\v 1 Haiwa Jehovha, regai kuramba munyerere;
\s Regai kuramba musingatauri, musanyarara Mwari.
\p
\v 2 Nokuti tarirai, vavengi venyu vanoita bope;
\s Vanokuvengai vakasimudza misoro yavo.
\p
\v 3 Vanofunga mano kuti vanyengere vanhu venyu,
\s Vanorangana pamusoro pavakavanzwa nemi.
\p
\v 4 Vakati, "Uyai, tivaparadze, varege kuzova rudzi;
\s Kuti zita raIsiraeri rirege kuzorangarirwa."
\p
\v 5 Nokuti vakarangana nomwoyo mumwe;
\s Vanoita sungano kuzorwa nemi.
\p
\v 6 Matende aEdhomu navaIshimaeri, Moabhu navaHagari;
\p
\v 7 Gebhari, naAmoni, naAmareki; Firisitia pamwechete navagere Tire;
\p
\v 8 Asiriawo wakasangana navo; Vakabatsira vana vaRoti.
\p
\v 9 Muvaitire sezvamakaitira Midhiani; NaSisera, naJabhini, paRwizi Kishoni;
\p
\v 10 Ivo vakaparadzwa paEndori;
\s Vakava mupfudze wapasi.
\p
\v 11 Itai vakuru vavo saOrebhi naZeebhi; iNkokwaruro , kx-vack_da (d.N
\v 0 OSZ saZebha naZarimuna;
\p
\v 12 Ivo vakati, "Ngatizvitorere Ugaro hwaMwari huve hwedu."
\p
\v 13 Mwari wangu, muvaite seguruva rinondeyeswa nemhepo;
\s Samakoto anodzingwa nemhepo.
\p
\v 14 Somoto unopisa dondo, Somurazvo womoto unopisa makomo;
\p
\v 15 Muvateverere saizvozvo nedutu renyu remhepo,
\s Muvavhunduse nechamupupuri chenyu.
\p
\v 16 Fukidzai zviso zvavo nokunyadziswa;
\s Kuti vatsvake zita renyu, Jehovha.
\p
\v 17 Ngavanyadziswe, vavhunduswe nokusingaperi;
\s Zvirokwazvo, ngavanyadziswe vafe;
\p
\v 18 Vazive kuti imi moga, imi
\s munezita rinonzi Jehovha, Ndimi Wokumusorosoro kumusoro
\s kwapasi pose.
